title: Ask HN: Best Laptop for Development?
text: I am in the market for a new laptop development PC. I typically use Windows as the host OS (for games etc.) and Linux VM’s for development work. Price and battery is less important (I usually go to places with power sockets). What do you guys recommend?

title: Tell HN: Windows 11 upgrade was offered to me on older hardware
text:
Upon logon I just had to carefully click through 3 screens of Windows 11 update "encouragement" on my 9 year old Dell Latitude E6540.

I thought I was safe on my older devices, but apparently I was wrong.
